## #1 — Heading-stack breadcrumb prefix (~half day)

### Goal
Embed a chunk under `H1 AMD > H2 Financial Statements > H3 Cash Flows` with
the full ancestor path, not just the immediate header.

### Files to modify

- `backend/src/doc_ir.rs:210` — extend `ChunkMeta`:
  ```rust
  pub heading_path: Vec<String>, // ["AMD", "Financial Statements", "Cash Flows"]
  ```
  Field is additive; existing `#[derive(Default)]` covers serde back-compat.

- `backend/src/memory/chunker_factory.rs:66-143` — in `chunk_ir`, maintain a
  `heading_stack: Vec<(u8, String)>` across the loop:
  - On `BlockType::Header { level }`: pop entries with `entry_level >= level`,
